cardVerificationMW.title: Verify Bank Card
cardVerificationMW.processDesc: Depending on the type of card selected, this will show you how the card should be positioned to create a verification photo

plasticInstruction.title: First way
plasticInstruction.first: open our site on your computer
plasticInstruction.second: take a picture of your card against it so that the card numbers can be read
plasticInstruction.notice: Important! The card numbers and owner's name should be visible on the photo. An open tab with the kassa.ss website should be visible behind the card

secondVariant.title: Second way
secondVariant.first: Write on a piece of paper the name of our site x-pay and today's date
secondVariant.second: Attach the card to the piece of paper and take a photo.
secondVariant.notice: It is important that the card numbers and the name of the owner are readable in the photo.

firstVariant.title: First way
firstVariant.first: open the virtual card on your computer.
firstVariant.second: in another window open our website (x-pay)
firstVariant.third: zoom out one of the windows on the screen so that both windows can be photographed
firstVariant.notice: Important! The card numbers and owner's name should be visible on the photo. An open tab with the kassa.ss website should be visible behind the card

secondVariant.title: Second way
secondVariant.third: take a photo of the virtual card with the x-pay tab open in the background
secondVariant.notice: Important! The card numbers and owner's name must be read on the photo.

thirdVariant.title: Third way
thirdVariant.first: open the virtual map on your phone or computer.
thirdVariant.second: write on a piece of paper the name of our site x-pay and today's date
thirdVariant.third: put a piece of paper on the screen and take a photo
thirdVariant.notice: Important! The card numbers and owner's name must be read on the photo.

confirm.title: Attention! Card verification.
confirm.content: This is the first time you make an exchange with this card on our service. For the security of your funds, verification of the Card is required. The procedure is one-time and takes from 1 to 5 minutes.

upload.title: Verification of cards
upload.description:
Please take a photo of your bank card with any device on the background of the monitor (screen) of the computer with the open tab of the x-pay website.
This is necessary for confirming the voluntary transfer of your funds from the card to make an exchange on our website.
upload.requirement1: On the photo card number and the name of the owner should be readable.
upload.requirement2: The monitor should be visible behind the card (in the background) with the open tab of the site x-pay

wait.content: We are awaiting the processing of an application for card verification. We will automatically notify you as soon as the application will be processed.

refProgramPage.title: Referral program
refProgramPage.subtitle: In order to take advantage of all the benefits of our service, you need to register on our website and activate your account by mail. To do this, you must specify personal and existing mail. Only one account can be linked to one mail. Before registering, read the rules of our service.
refProgramPage.termsRefProgram:
Terms of referral accruals for your referrals' exchanges:
- 0.5% of the exchange amount after their registration on the site;
- 0.6% of the exchange amount for 20 invited referrals;
- 0.8% of the exchange amount for 50 invited referrals;
- 0.9% of the exchange amount for 100 invited referrals;
- 1% of the exchange amount from the exchange amount for 300 invited referrals.

A mandatory condition is the activity and reality of the invited referral, who must carry out exchange transactions for amounts exceeding 5,000 rubles or their equivalent in other currencies.

ReferalList.title: Seznam Vašich referencí
ReferalList.content: Popis našeho referenčního programu: Jsme přední mezinárodní poskytovatel směnárenských služeb v oblasti elektronických peněz. Zajišťujeme směnu, vklady a výběry následujících valut: Perfect Money, BTC, kódy BTC-e, Payeer, QIWI, Yandex.Money. Zajišťujeme rovněž provádění bankovních převodů. Spolupracujeme s takovými bankami jako jsou Sberbank, Alfa Bank, VTB24 a Tinkoff.

rewardsRequest.needСonfirmation:
O bezpečnost našeho účtu nám jde na prvním místě. Pro dokončení požadavku o výplatu odměn jsme na Vaši adresu odeslali zprávu s odkazem, který slouží k potvrzení zadání požadavku. Máte-li jakékoli otázky či v případě, že dojde ke zpoždění platby, obraťte se prosím na naši technickou podporu.

refPage.shareSocials: O Váš odkaz se můžete rychle podělit prostřednictvím sociálních sítí:

shareText.common: Ahoj! Našel jsem na internetu výbornou službu umožňující rychlou a bezpečnou výměnu peněz. Zajdi na stránku, registruj se a hned přímo ode mě dostaneš slevu 5 % na jakýkoliv druh směny! Taky ti jdou z každé směny přes můj odkaz bonusy, a od 5 pozvaných osob dál se dávají dárky (na seznamu je iPad mini)
